---
title: Scenario 12 — FLIP Generation Guard (Stale Capture Discarded)
---
sequenceDiagram
    participant Service as Backend Service
    participant Cache as SourceCache
    participant Box as OrderedAnimatedListBox
    participant Pipeline as Pipeline
    participant FLIP as FLIP Engine

    Service->>Cache: Order change #1
    Cache-->>Box: CollectionChanged (Move) after throttle

    Box->>Pipeline: Enqueue OrderChange#1
    Pipeline->>Box: ProcessSnapshot(OrderChange#1)

    Box->>FLIP: OnBeforeAnimatedDiff()\nCapturePreLayoutBounds()\ncapturedGeneration = ++_flipGeneration  [gen=1]

    Box->>Box: DiffVisible(order#1)\nVisibleItems reordered
    Note over FLIP: ApplyFlip posted at DispatcherPriority.Render\n(not yet fired — layout pass pending)

    Note over Box: Before Render priority fires...

    Service->>Cache: Order change #2 (rapid)
    Cache-->>Box: CollectionChanged (Move) after throttle

    Box->>Box: ClassifyChange → OrderChange
    Box->>Pipeline: Check queue for existing OrderChange\nFound — replace with #2

    Note over Pipeline: Queue: [OrderChange#2]\n(#1 collapsed into #2)

    Box->>Box: _inflightCount reaches 0 from #1 processing
    Box->>Pipeline: OnAllAnimationsComplete\n_pipelineBusy = false
    Pipeline->>Pipeline: TryProcessNext\nDequeue OrderChange#2\n_pipelineBusy = true

    Box->>FLIP: OnBeforeAnimatedDiff()\nCapturePreLayoutBounds() — fresh capture\ncapturedGeneration = ++_flipGeneration  [gen=2]

    Box->>Box: DiffVisible(order#2)

    Note over FLIP: Now the Render priority post from gen=1 fires...
    FLIP->>FLIP: ApplyFlip — check capturedGeneration(1) == _flipGeneration(2)?
    Note over FLIP: 1 != 2 → STALE CAPTURE\nReturn immediately, do nothing

    Note over FLIP: The gen=2 ApplyFlip fires next...
    FLIP->>FLIP: ApplyFlip — check capturedGeneration(2) == _flipGeneration(2)?
    Note over FLIP: 2 == 2 → VALID\nProceed with FLIP animation

    FLIP->>FLIP: Animate items from captured positions\nto new layout positions

    Note over Box: Result: Only one FLIP plays\nto the correct final order.\nStale capture from gen=1 was\ndiscarded without any visual glitch.
